# - Try to find the KDEWIN library
# 
# used environment vars 
#  KDEWIN_DIR  - kdewin root dir 
#
# this will define
#  KDEWIN_FOUND - system has KDEWIN
#  KDEWIN_DIR - the KDEWIN root installation dir
